name: Sergeant Preston of the Yukon
overview: Canadian Mountie Sgt. Preston patrols the wilds of the Yukon with his horse Rex and his faithful dog Yukon King, battling both the elements and criminals.

episodes.name: The Mad Wolf of Lost Canyon
Escape to the North
episodes.overview: Two hold-up men - one wounded - force their company on an old   ex-convict friend who is now going straight. They threaten to   reveal his past to his young daughter unless he helps them by   getting medical aid.
